Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, she calls {\i1}this{\i0} all alone in a hotel room?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? I got dropped? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess these things happen once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as I wasn't\Nout grinding, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Towel, towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.78,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Wrong password"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Did I mistype it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.17,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Wrong password"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.05,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Wrong password"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, some net games, including {\i1}LA{\i0},\Nhave been rife with account hacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone take appropriate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... I've been had!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.11,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Wrong password"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So right now, someone other than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...is on as Rusian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.88,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"LV. 08: I thought I was giving up\Nbeing a net game husband?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako! That isn't me! It's an impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That must have been\Na shock, huh? It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a look at your chat log, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us are now all alone, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, I want to exchange some couple's chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Couple's, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, so we're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, after all this time,\Nwhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember the day when we had\Nour wedding in the church, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of that day,\Neven now, I feel enraptured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're already good to go, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get this started, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That "couple's chat"\Nyou were just talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Y-You're being\Nunusually assertive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you like that? Don't you like {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Rusian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am. Do I look any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know! Before we start,\Nsend me a pic of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something a little sexy\Nthat I can use on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm not too concerned\Nabout your looks, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicks that play net games\Nare all dowdy, nerdy losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! Don't say things\Nlike that using Rusian's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Face" nothing... I {\i1}am{\i0} Rusian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My beloved Rusian wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian wouldn't say those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.40,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(300,60)}"Ako: Please stop! Don't say\Nthings like that using Rusian's face!\NRusian: "Face" nothing... I {\i1}am{\i0} Rusian.\NAko: My beloved Rusian wouldn't...\NAko: Rusian wouldn't say those things!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, you haven't done a single\Nthing you need to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that\Nisn't supposed to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but in net games, it sometimes does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, you're the victim here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,being pressured by the nasty chat\Nof some troll looking to hook up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so you did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, if anyone is to blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's me for being so careless\Nand letting it happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, there's nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I called someone who wasn't you "Rusian,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and just for a short while, I thought it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to be careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but who would have thought we'd\Nactually have an account hacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't laugh it off when it\Nhappens to someone close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When connecting from a PC\Nthat anyone could use,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we should have been more\Nthan sufficiently cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. This is my fault, since I set this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NMaster, you're not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing to do is contact the hotel\Nand tell them what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I arranged to have my password reset,\Nand got my account back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it was that\Nyou had your password stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the PC in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then the first time\Nit didn't take your password,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't because you mistyped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The page that was open on the lobby PC
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was a fake login page that\Nlooked just like the official one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I logged in with it,\Nit stole the ID and password I entered,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then forwarded me to\Nthe legitimate, official page.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A classic phishing scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how bad is the damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:37.15,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Character not yet created\NCreate a new character"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian has been erased, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I disappeared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But my Rusian is...\NMy Rusian is no longer there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's {\i1}mine{\i0}. He's {\i1}my{\i0} Rusian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do\Nabout him being erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can make a new character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to start looking for the things\Nthat I {\i1}can't{\i0} ever get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The items that Rusian was carrying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He apparently realized what I was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I went to recover\Nmy items right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of them were already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy works fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that it's a\Ncontest of speed for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably sold off my items,\Nso I'll buy back as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to give money to a hacker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's galling to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do want to at least\Nget back my keepsake items.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go check out\Nthe shops and markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can we do? I'll drum up some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me reach out to some people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone go back\Nto the PCs in their rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and hunt for the stolen items.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go consult with a friend of mine\Nwho knows the most people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An account hack, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Having your gear taken away\Nand your character erased
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is a dreadful thing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm logging in using a sub-character\Nthat I created a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and my name is Piroshiki-{\i1}kun{\i0} now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but please call me Rusian.\NI'm more accustomed to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, you were careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One must protect oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe self-defense is basic to net gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that quite well.\NSo, while this might sound brazen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you'd\Nhelp find my stolen items--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not. I didn't think--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean you'll help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before?\NWe're all fellow game players here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When a fellow player is\Nin trouble, we help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be a net gamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Nekohime-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, you heard her, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Nekohime's Elite Guard,\Nwe will find the stolen items!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Nekohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Nekohime!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I-I'm happy that you will help {\i1}meow{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't have to rile\Nyourselves up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Does anything look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that this assortment of items
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,were part of what was in my inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This seller's name is... Rontan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this is the one that hacked my account?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll submit a screengrab of this\Nto admins, as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken one. But he's\Ncharging a pretty penny for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.\NI'll buy them back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, you don't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do this. It will help\Nalleviate some of the guilt I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you have mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Cloud, of Nekohime's Elite Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.27,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Attached item\NPair ring"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...the ring I gave you, Rusian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he got it after slaying a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been thrown away,\Nsince it couldn't be sold,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and that monster picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrown away? How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mean, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a result, it came back to us.\NThis is a minor miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is! This is the power of our love at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.60,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Staff Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishimura-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that what happened may be a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't let it get you down too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The school during summer vacation\Nsure is a quiet place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming with me to explain\Nwhat happened to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NIt happened during a club camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As club president, it's only\Nright that I accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I am so upset by this,\Nit surprises even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As you should be. You had your items stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the character you\Nwere so attached to erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that, too, but even worse than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand that he posed as Rusian\Nand talked to Ako like he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole Rusian. And for a short while,\Nhe stole my Ako, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the drawbacks of net relations
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is not always being able\Nto confirm who someone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can take someone's account from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easy to become someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more so in net games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew the ties we had to each\Nother were so fragile and insecure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako knew that Rusian was someone else\Nfrom only a conversation in print.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How deep a relationship do you have\Nwhere someone else's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can be determined from that\Ntiny bit of communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to say that\Nproves how solid your ties are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're starting to cheer up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but as a result, I want to\Nget this bastard that much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out for blood right from the start, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What do you mean,\Nthe admins aren't budging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got someone selling\Nthe stolen items as a set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how you cut it,\Nthat guy's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who did the hacking had an IP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't match Rontan,\Nthe one selling the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,IP?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,An IP...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a little like a personal\Nnumber that everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.78,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Net"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,who connects to the net has set for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you do something bad, it can\Nbe used to identify you, and catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we can identify them\Nas being the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't accuse them of any crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably normally\Nplays the game from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but when he does account\Nhacking or other dicey stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he uses some other IP.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do, grin and bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for interrupting you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,while you are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've discovered some somewhat bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you take a look at this URL?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"LON's Scam Blog"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.24,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"LON's Scam Blog"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The blog of a famous swindler\Nwho runs scams on all sorts of games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He jokes about when he hacked\Nyour account on there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Screw that [oink] bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to mash the [oink] out of that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not printing those\Nwords in the chat window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy really is a nauseating piece of [oink].
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a show-off miscreant who can't\Nhelp but announce his misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of these types on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which, he also\Napparently dabbles in RMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he seems to be careful\Nenough not to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,RMT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what that is, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Real money trades--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the act of exchanging in-game money\Nor items for real-life cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In {\i1}LA{\i0}, it's against the terms of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds as though you had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure whether it will work or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but we might be able to at least\Ncatch that swindling bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishimura is making us\Ncook something like this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If this doesn't work,\Nhe'd better say his prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been up overnight\Nthree days straight, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sounds like someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dropped by--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you close the door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what kind of treatment was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was just reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife has come to the family home,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so you might offer her a\Nwarm welcome, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're not my wife anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the moment Rusian vanished,\Nour marriage was annulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're divorced?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian disappearing was such a shock to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're not married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could that phony Rusian\Ndo something like this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew he was such a villain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It took you long enough to get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that right now...\NWhat {\i1}is{\i0} our relationship, Rusian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if we're no longer a married couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then is this no longer welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what it is you're up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are working so hard,\NI thought I would make you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what I\Nwould do about lunch! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, after I eat this,\NI'm ready for the final stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Um...\N--Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're working hard,\Nbut please don't overdo it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rusian, having you stay well is\Nthe most important thing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, of all the things you've ever said,\Nthat was the most wife-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Wanna-be-Famous Swindler's Blog."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I get an email from someone saying\Nthey found a blog better than mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I take a peek\Nto see what it's all about,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of cheap knockoff do I find?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From the Nekohime's Elite Guard\Nmembership fee collection scam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to swindling the Black Magician\Nout of rare items...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's not too shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a trading board here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seeking RMTs in {\i1}LA{\i0}," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These rates aren't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time. Is everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Target confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The character's name is Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko is even more ridiculous than LON.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.39,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Trade Request"\N"Decline" "Accept"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission is proceeding\Nto Phase 2. Plan N, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening with Plan N?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for the admins to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to wait much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. A little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Gamemaster Nyack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why the two of you\Nwere transferred here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The administrators have received word
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that the two of you are\Nengaging in RMT activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--What do you mean--\N--Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This person contacted me on a trading board,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and was indeed about to\Nengage in RMT with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You set me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who set me up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not that guy from\Nthe other day, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, what does an attempted RMT\Nwhere no money changed hands prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At most, it warrants a\None-week account lockout, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have also been accused of\Naccount hacking via the character "Rontan."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rontan? Who cares about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the IP submitted\Nfrom the trading board,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we have determined that you have\Ncommitted illegal access violations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and are considering filing charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't buffalo me!\NThere's no way a site that dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to turn IPs over to any administrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so you thought,\Nand that's when you got sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} site--one that\NI put up three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NThat site has posts going back for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, was it ever a lot of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,fabricating several years' worth\Nof authentic-sounding posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...you faked an entire {\i1}site{\i0} just to set me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You wasted that much time\Njust to trick one person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I am. Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that after you made my\Nwife cry, you weren't going to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason you all stayed up nights\Nwas to make that fake site?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We have him logged
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:55.43,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Rontan" "Write Logs" "Illegal Access"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,responding to that trade request\Nfrom home, not knowing it was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he showed up as the\Ncharacter Shoko for the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:22:05.44,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Rontan" "Write Logs" "Illegal Access"\N"Shoko"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever he did anything dodgy,\Nhe was careful to use a separate IP.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Including, of course,\Nwhen he hacked my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The admins took the gracious\Nstep of locking Rusian's--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Piroshiki-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s account for\Nthree days for an attempted RMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready for a much\Nstricter punishment, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that they also\Nrestored Rusian's character.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that Nyack guy is seriously dreamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that my Rusian\Nis coming back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's still one last matter remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, I know it's late to bring this up now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but when my account was hacked,\NI was honestly shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like just by having\Nsomeone else get on as Rusian,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the relationship that you and I\Nhave was also being taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ever want to go through that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be closer,\N{\i1}closer{\i0} to you than before. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...would you like not {\i1}Rusian{\i0}, in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.20,0:23:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but {\i1}me{\i0}, in real life, just a little bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I can't like you a little bit more,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because I already love you so much now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:20.08,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"I thought if we stayed over,\Nwe would get along better?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After what happened, I came up\Nwith a foolproof anti-hacking measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--What is it?\N--We just have to buy out the whole hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--You can't do that.\N--Then we'll buy up the net circuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--You can't!\N--Even better, the admin team!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
